  "title": "🍸BARTENDERS @ BUGIS | FROM $2.3K + ALLOWANCE | TRANSPORT PROVIDED",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>🍸BARTENDERS @ BUGIS | FROM $2.3K + ALLOWANCE | TRANSPORT PROVIDED </strong></u></p><p>📍Location: Bugis  </p><p>💰Salary: $2.3k-$2.5k + Night shift allowance of up to $400/month (depending on the outlet)  </p><p>🕑Shift hours: 6.30pm-3.30am + minimum of 4h OT per week </p><p>44h per week </p><p>🗓️Working days:  </p><p>6 days a week </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Interact with customers to create a fun and welcoming atmosphere  </p></li><li><p>Prepare the spirits, mixers and garnishes for drinks before customers enter </p></li><li><p>Make drinks for customers, including customised orders </p></li><li><p>Ensure the bar is clean and ready for guests  </p></li></ul><p>Requirements:  </p><ul><li><p>Food and hygiene safety certificate </p></li><li><p>Minimum 1 year experience as a bartender </p></li><li><p>Able to work night shifts  </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*<em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </em></p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
